Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.50,0:00:13.50,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doryo Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.59,0:00:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll go if you're a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna change\Nyour whole world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a lesson...\NMy mom's gonna yell at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.70,Menacing,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*Irritated*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoulder wheel backdrop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.45,0:00:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he can't swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.67,0:00:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He came to!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.29,0:00:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Again! Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.51,0:01:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! He's addicted now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kao-chan, we came\Nto pay you a visit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:45.94,Twitch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kou         Tsubaki         Watari
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The nape of her neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ever heard of knocking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her skin's so fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delete that memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow, what a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can never\Nbe anyone's bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:58.42,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuhara University Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really threw us a curve,\Ngetting hospitalized like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my dad's so over-the-top.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only here for routine\Ntesting, just to make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever passed\Nout like that before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been a little anemic,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but this is a good chance\Nto get thoroughly tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I pushed\Nmyself a little too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, all that violin practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,not to mention chasing after\NMr. Escape Artist... all week long!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:33.08,Menacing,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*Looming*
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:34.93,Clang,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*Drip Drip Drip*
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The stress of not being able\Nto rehearse together, and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaori and I didn't make\Nit to the next round.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unprecedented. One mishap after another.\N A no-brainer for disqualification.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:04:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ineligible. Performance interrupted.\NThe worst possible scenario. All my fault.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You haven't said a\Nword of reproach.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't outstay our welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat? I'm gonna spend the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Kao-chan, see you at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm staying over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, you aren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been playing the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It would be so much easier if\Nshe just chewed me out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. I haven't been playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like... I have nothing to\Noffer but my piano playing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a bad thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you'll\Nbe able to forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gray skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:18.01,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuhara University Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like rain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, hurry up!\NWhat, you're not there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What were you talking\Nabout with Kao-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, not anything major...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you shouldn't mind telling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Ryo-chin. Yeah, yeah.\N You busy right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is playing the piano all I have to offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all. You have lots\Nof good qualities, Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey! Look\Nat that! The sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A sunny spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you'll\Nbe able to forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see me make the shot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending this to Kaori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.37,0:06:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop by the\Nhospital tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear she's getting\Ndischarged the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get her a\Npresent on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So he already knows\Nher email address...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she'll get a\Nkick out of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna pass. You\Nshould go by yourself, Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm the one who made a\Nfiasco out of her competition.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And besides...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:06:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one she leaned on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's only because I'm\Nthe one who can play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's all there is to it.\N No other reason.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I know. I know that, but still.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know that but\Nyou'll never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold back because\Nof me. Let's go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We might catch her naked again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watari! The captain shouldn't be slacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch all the\Ndazzling plays I make!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's pretty pumped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You got that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our final tournament's\Nabout to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, after witnessing that spectacle,\Nhow can I not get all fired up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The way you two were that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's burned into my mind!\NI'll never forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll never forget it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you'll\Nbe able to forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The piano is just one part of you.\NBut in that moment, without a doubt...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The piano was everything to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you're trying to rip that away by force.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As if you were plucking off your limbs...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why it hurts too much for you to bear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your face says the suffering is so painful,\N too painful to bear...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you think you'll be able to forget? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:09:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, not a chance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you and I are\Nliving for that moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were great,\Nmiddle school duo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're a musician, just like me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, pianist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unprecedented. One mishap after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the people here won't ever forget us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget, even if I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you accompanied me.\NBecause you played the piano for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kousei Arima.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's merciless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That unbending gaze.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even from the back,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she won't let me give up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please support me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one who was being supported...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:10:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...was me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you. Thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So I\Npassed out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First... Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that, Tsubaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.61,0:11:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Little kids are so gung-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know, even though\Nthe water's so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but you used to dive from the\N"Courage Bridge" all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, always\Nshoving Arima-kun off it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was no biggie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei always laughed it off himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't call that "no biggie."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sure it was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know it for a fact.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen\Nbetween you and Arima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-N-Not a thing! Don't\Nsay freaky things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:33.10,Grab,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{*Oyoyo*}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:33.10,Twitch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nailed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, being upbeat is\Nyour only saving grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But yesterday and today, you kind\Nof haven't been yourself. Tsubaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are cloudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't Kashiwagi and Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Saito-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, check out that uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.43,0:13:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's a high school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you\Nsince graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You burning up the league as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm on fire! How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough being a first year\Nagain. I'm nothing but a gofer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if they'd just let me play\Nshortstop, I'd be the best, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The former captain of\Nour baseball team.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Totally hot, dependable, and the\None all the girls dreamed about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So unlike someone else I know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A complete tool,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}not to be depended on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one's idea of a dreamboat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's okay. It's okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I do know that Kousei has lots of good\Nqualities besides playing the piano, after all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like rain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloudy weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are cloudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's okay. It's okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So why am I feeling\Nso uneasy, then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsubaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This was no coincidence, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The former captain of our baseball\Nteam. Totally hot, dependable,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the one all the girls dreamed about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I dreamed about him, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I was never able to tell him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and my love melted away with the\Nsnow on graduation day, and it was over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the kind of\Nlove I thought it was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm happy. I'm so happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm serious\Nabout this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yet why... why isn't my\Nheart sparkling, I wonder?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet if this was\Nback around graduation,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my heart would've been\Nsparkling like a starry sky in winter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So she's out of the hospital.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't get the wrong idea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She just needed an accompanist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hop, skip, jump! Hop, skip, jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As if you can see right\Nthrough me, into my heart...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hop, skip... hop, skip...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always, out of nowhere, you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hop...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skip...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...just show up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.28,0:16:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Playing hopscotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was\Nwaiting for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:16:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you holding out your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My gift for getting out of the hospital.\N I'll take it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's horrible of you!\NWatari-kun gave me flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you're the one who made\Nsuch a mess of my performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I was gunning to win it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make women cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is why men are so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then! I'll do something for you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll do anything I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, what should I ask for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enter a piano competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? You were\Nplaying fine that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again,\Nlooking down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're all afraid, you know... \Nto get up onstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you'll mess up.\NMaybe they'll totally reject you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you grit your teeth\Nand get up onstage anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something compels us...\Nmoves us to play music.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it like that for you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything you say and do...\Nit all sparkles so brightly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too blinding for me,\Nand I end up closing my eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...who hurled my precious\Nsheet music away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't deserve to\Nbe a performer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I played with all my might because I\Nwanted my mother to get well, and yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are tons of musicians\Nin the same boat. I'm sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ones who think, "I'll be darned if I do\Nthis," or "Why don't you play it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you pick it up again...\Nand you sit before that score.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...you create the most\Nbeautiful lie of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're still only 14, you know!\NLet's pull out all the stops, and dive right in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bombs away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Glug!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, that was scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so good!\N I've always wanted to try that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything you say and do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It all sparkles so brightly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too blinding for me, and\NI end up closing my eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I can't help\Naspiring to be like you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you'll be able to forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That moment, when my\Nmusic reached them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna change your whole world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I\Ncould ever forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scary stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way I\Ncould ever forget.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I'm a musician,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}just like you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.51,0:21:20.02,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gray Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are your glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:38.86,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 6\NWay Back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.03,0:22:55.10,BTSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watch Again Next Week!
